TxService->>LogService: redo req
LogService->>BraftStateMachine: redirect redo req
Note right of BraftStateMachine: serialize redo_req into raft log\nand bind raft log into braft::task
BraftStateMachine->>BraftService: apply the braft::task
BraftService->BraftService: distributed persist the raft log and\nwait for the ack from majority nodes
BraftService->>BraftStateMachine: call braft::on_apply interface to\niterate all the accepted raft logs
BraftStateMachine->>LogState: update the log state based on the new raft log
BraftStateMachine->>TxService: return the response to TxService by Closure 
